speak to the

00:34:31.800 --> 00:34:33.990
spirit of fear

00:34:33.990 --> 00:34:34.000
and command

00:34:34.000 --> 00:34:36.750
it

00:35:02.920 --> 00:35:05.750
to release them.

00:35:20.920 --> 00:35:23.630
I cover you

00:35:23.640 --> 00:35:25.950
with the blood and thank you, Lord, that

00:35:38.800 --> 00:35:41.270
the light that pierces

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:44.109
all darkness

00:35:44.119 --> 00:35:46.230
is shining on

00:36:07.800 --> 00:36:10.470
you.

00:36:30.040 --> 00:36:32.510
We thank you

00:36:32.520 --> 00:36:36.030
for creative ideas for soul-winning. We thank

00:36:36.040 --> 00:36:38.750
you

00:37:01.349 --> 00:37:01.359
that

00:37:22.640 --> 00:37:25.230
we have

00:37:37.680 --> 00:37:39.910
a better covenant

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:42.230
through Jesus

00:37:44.750 --> 00:37:44.760
Christ.

00:37:46.440 --> 00:37:49.670
In

00:37:53.309 --> 00:37:53.319
Jesus'name,

00:37:55.800 --> 00:37:58.390
amen.

00:37:58.400 --> 00:38:01.030
Put a

00:38:01.040 --> 00:38:03.790
smile on your face and a song in your

00:38:03.800 --> 00:38:06.430
heart. Jesus

00:38:06.430 --> 00:38:06.440
loves

00:38:06.440 --> 00:38:08.950
you, and we will see you next time.

00:38:11.520 --> 00:38:14.079
Bye-bye.

